Package: aisdk.datatools
Title: Data-Science Agent Tools for the 'aisdk' Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yonghe", "Xia", , "xiayh17@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R-native data-science tooling for 'aisdk' agents. Provides a
    structured 'ggplot2' chart schema and renderer, a 'knitr'-based reporting
    engine, autonomous data-science pipelines, a code sandbox, and R
    environment/object introspection tools that agents can call to inspect data
    and produce artifacts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
